 The calculation of these terms are same with before
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{D_{B}^{3}}{D_{\phi}D_{\Lambda}^{4}}=\frac{(D_{\phi}+m_{\phi}^{2}+M_{1}^{2}-M_{2}^{2}-2p_{1}.k)^{3}}{D_{\phi}D_{\Lambda}^{4}}
\]

